# Immutable Domain Boundaries

We operate two completely isolated zones. Never cross-link or proxy between them.

- Zone A: `cabin-rentals-of-georgia.com`. Next.js App Router storefront. Guest-facing, SEO-optimized, highly cached.
- Zone B: `crog-ai.com`. Next.js Command Center. Protected by `GlobalAuthMiddleware`. Staff and AI agents only.
